        depends on MV_ETH_PNC_PARSER
        int "Use PnC for extra ETYPE detection"
        default 0
        ---help---
        Number of extra ETYPEs can be detected in addition to 
	ARP, IPv4, IPv6, PPPoE are detected by default.

